AAPL Stock Price:$150 Target Reiterated By Wedbush

The introduction of three new Macs featuring Apple\xe2\x80\x99s breakthrough M1 chip represents a bold change that was years in the making# and marks a truly historic day for the Mac and for Apple#said Apple\xe2\x80\x99s CEO Tim Cook in a statement.M1 is by far the most powerful chip we\xe2\x80\x99ve ever created.

At the event today#Apple had announced a new MacBook Air#a 13-inch MacBook Pro# and a new Mac mini.The Apple M1 chip delivers up to a 3.5x faster CPU#a 6x faster GPU#up to 2x longer battery life#and up to 15x faster machine learning.
